  - display __inline_show_109_1/display-byte-helper: 999999 steps; display is not repeated often enough for a shared display-byte helper
  - display __inline_show_109_1/display-byte-builder: 999999 steps; display has no literal/X2-sensitive fragments to build

Cell Roles:
