  - dispatch@49/indirect-register-flow: 35 steps; rejected; selector is key-valued, not address-valued, and building an address register would not beat the compare-chain
  - dispatch@49/dark-indirect-table: 7 steps; considered; layout proof did not establish a conflict-free address/data table for this site
  - dispatch@49/super-dark-dispatch: 6 steps; considered; selector is key-valued, and layout proof did not place one-command cases at 48..53 with tails at 01..06
  - display __inline_show_43_0/decimal-pack: 10 steps; ordinary decimal field packing was not the cheapest display strategy

Cell Roles:
  01: 5E address, constant, overlay - address can be reused as constant; code/data overlay allowed
